# Frontend environment variables (Vite / browser-side only)
# See docs/DEPLOYMENT.md for details.
#
# In local development, leave all values blank - Vite proxies /api/* to
# the backend dev server at 127.0.0.1:8787 automatically.
#
# In production, the frontend Cloudflare Worker proxies /api/* to the
# backend via a service binding. No URL configuration is needed.
#
# Only set VITE_API_BASE_URL if you deploy the backend on a completely
# separate origin without a service binding or Vite proxy.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
#
# Note: API_ACCESS_TOKEN is a Worker-side secret, not a Vite variable.
# It is set in the Cloudflare dashboard and injected by the frontend
# Worker - never exposed to the browser. See docs/DEPLOYMENT.md.
